                     Macross Digital Mission VF-X
                       Control List version 1.0
                  by Lacano (lacano@worldnet.att.net)

FIGHTER MODE (Type A)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Control Pad Up           Nose Down
Control Pad Down         Nose Up
Control Pad Left         Barrel Roll Left
Control Pad Right        Barrel Roll Right

Select                   Change View (cockpit or behind)
Start                    Pause

L1                       Throttle Up
L2                       Throttle Down

L1 (x2)                  Afterburner
L2 (x2)                  Quick Stop

R1                       Deadly Technique Shift (see below)                       
R2                       -------- (not used)

R1+(Left or Right)       Left or Right Yaw (sp?)

O                        Lock on + Missile
X                        Vulcan Cannon
Sq                       Transformation B (F -> G)  
Tr                       Transformation A (F -> B) 


GERWALK MODE (Type A)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Control Pad Up           Nose Down
Control Pad Down         Nose Up
Control Pad Left         Slide Left
Control Pad Right        Slide Roll Right

Select                   Change View (cockpit or behind)
Start                    Pause

L1                       Throttle Up
L2                       Throttle Down

L1 (x2)                  --------
L2 (x2)                  --------

(L1 or L2)+(L or R)      Turn Left or Right

R1                       Deadly Technique Shift (see below)                       
R2                       --------

R1+(Left or Right)       --------

O                        Lock on + Missile
X                        Vulcan Cannon
Sq                       Transformation B (G -> B)
Tr                       Transformation A (G -> F)


BATTOROID MODE (Type A)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Control Pad Up           Move Forward
Control Pad Down         Move Backward
Control Pad Left         Turn Left
Control Pad Right        Turn Right

Select                   Change View (cockpit or behind)
Start                    Pause

L1                       Shift
L2                       Shift

L1 (x2)                  --------
L2 (x2)                  --------

(L1 or L2)+(L or R)      Slide Left or Right

R1                       Deadly Technique Shift (see below)                       
R2                       Not used

R1+(Left or Right)       --------

O                        Change Aiming
X                        Vulcan Cannon
Sq                       Transformation B (B -> F)
Tr                       Transformation A (B -> G)


CONTROL TYPE B
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Everything is the same except the four thumb buttons.

O                        Transformation A
X                        Transformation B
Sq                       Vulcan Cannon
Tr                       Missiles


CONTROL TYPE C
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Everything is the same except the four thumb buttons.

O                        Transformation B
X                        Vulcan Cannon
Sq                       Missiles
Tr                       Transformation A


DEADLY TECHNIQUES
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Press the R1 button to activate the Deadly Technique menu which will 
appear in the upper right hand corner.  Each of the four thumb buttons 
is mapped to a different technique with the cost of the technique on 
the right had side.  The total number of points allocated to these 
techniques is superimposed on the picture of the four buttons.

The techniques are specific to which transformation you are in and on 
the mech you are using.


